{"tid":2019172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國外交部回應監警會報告 促港府就警隊責任展開「有力、獨立」調查","createTime":"2020-05-16T05:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T15:15:34.000Z","uid":70063,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f1b96a8bb3f9c25a2fab329252ee59b4110f31","tid":2019172,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/UKinHongKong/status/1261480993363341312?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUKinHongKong%2Fstatus%2F1261480993363341312%3Fs%3D19&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=4ac7c9bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUKinHongKong%2Fstatus%2F1261480993363341312%3Fs%3D19&h=01a60136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/UKinHongKong/status/1261480993363341312?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n監警會發表長達一千頁報告，審視&nbsp;7.21 元朗襲擊「警黑勾結」、8.31 太子站「打死人」傳聞等事件，結論幾乎一面倒傾向警方立場。英國外交部發言人周五（15日）回應，會仔細審視報告的結論，並促請港府當局就警隊責任問題展開「有力、獨立」的調查（robust，independent inquiry）。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部周五發稿，回應香港監警會的審視報告。英國外交部發言人表示，警隊問責仍是重建香港信任的必要因素，英方會仔細審視報告的結論。外交部又重申，英國促請香港當局就警隊責任問題展開「有力、獨立」的調查。<br />\n<br />\n監警會去年七月設立專案組，審視反修例示威大型公眾活動，至昨日發表長達一千頁的報告，其中六個日期有獨立章節，包括 7.21 元朗襲擊、8.31 太子站警察襲擊市民事件、6.12 政總附近衝突等，但報告被質疑一面倒採納警方說法，內容偏頗。民陣召集人岑子杰批評報告刻意模糊警暴問題，亦無評價警方是否使用過份武力，認為只有獨立調查委員會，才能還原真相。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E4%BF%83%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%B1%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C-%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9B-%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E9%2580%25B2%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258A%259B-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=c99f3b47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E9%2580%25B2%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258A%259B-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%2F&h=77dbbda0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E4%BF%83%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%B1%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C-%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9B-%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"8775317070dbcb7273f67ee623ec4b94dae9d1a0","tid":2019172,"uid":24140,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"香港人就黎死撚哂啦<br />\n班左膠涼夠冷氣未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311bd9be9a64a43a746375eca73036093f68dc45","tid":2019172,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"林鄭仲問肥彭點平息示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d5df6b354ea5eee121b8a11e0b9c04a5873209","tid":2019172,"uid":288707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"唔係話一國兩制運作良好咩？"},{"pid":"7a7ef096d13cf97b0922ed290e444e07a6ab7eae","tid":2019172,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8775317070dbcb7273f67ee623ec4b94dae9d1a0","tid":2019172,"uid":24140,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"