al for rebuilding trust in Hong Kong. We will consider the conclusions of this report carefully.<br />\n<br />\nAs we have consistently stated, we urge the authorities to facilitate a robust, independent inquiry.<br />\n<br />\nFurther Information<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/foreign-office-statement-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fforeign-office-statement-on-hong-kong&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=5e3420f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/foreign-office-statement-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"9a0077c73f97872867b55f79996904ee9ad53b52","tid":2019172,"uid":5733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:18:28.000Z","msg":"屌真係好撚煩，日日都出來回應，淨係得把口零實事"},{"pid":"1eebbc08d903e21849a583ffaa91a42e977c2a31","tid":2019172,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c5dbe3b920a50b88abdf1c624b9e06f4e5e8208","tid":2019172,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8775317070dbcb7273f67ee623ec4b94dae9d1a0","tid":2019172,"uid":24140,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"香港人就黎死撚哂啦<br />\n班左膠涼夠冷氣未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:17:27.000Z","msg":"因為英國係香港利益唔夠,你唔係覺得香港會慘過新疆下話,佢係因為人道理由幫一早幫撚左新疆啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"笑撚左 講到香港搞成今日咁英國冇責任咁"},{"pid":"76eaa00d6844a462087df065b5fe1afe0cdf63da","tid":2019172,"uid":288393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"幾時先有黑色騎士團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6571a5c7c550c42c9ab8e2dea2ae01ac9ad15bab","tid":2019172,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3AnSMmG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.